limiting number of devices that can access network via an interface

--possible penalities
errordisabled state
shutdown state

--implementations(interface states)
static--assigned by admin
dynamic--allow whatever comes
sticky--stick to the one it learns first

interface fa0/1--///activate interface
switchport mode access--///optional coz ports are access(not trunk) by default
switchport security--///activate security on interface
switchport port-security maximum 1--///max number of devices allowed on interface
switchport port-security mac-address sticky/static
switchport portsecurity violation protect/restrict/shutdown --///add violation->implementation

show portsecurity interface fa0/1--///check security details on interface
